{"tid":1056871,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［娛樂圈最大黑幕］英皇整容奀星又奪風雲榜年度新人奬","createTime":"2019-03-11T13:22:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-11T13:34:12.000Z","uid":132432,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5d8b8d0748d635aa5fa7122a0330e2e0834cff92","tid":1056871,"uid":132432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T13:22:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YsSQLot.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYsSQLot.png&h=7bd32478&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有留意開香港樂壇既巴絲打應該都對曾樂彤呢個名唔陌生啦<br />\n今次佢又榮獲KKBOX香港風雲榜既年度新人<br />\n無料KOL係短短一年間掃哂樂壇咁多大奬 廣告資源<br />\n源源不絕 相信有好多人都好唔服<br />\n如果你話靠個樣 大把人靚過佢<br />\n如果你話靠把聲 街邊求其搵個都唱得好聽過佢<br />\n今時今日嘅香港樂壇<br />\n已經唔再需要唱歌好聽 有音樂造詣 有特殊才華既人先做到歌手<br />\n只需要識做世界女再執下個樣 再靠下運氣 同埋厚面皮就有機會㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"519d0083e95d60caaa16e7a162cd85450b345923","tid":1056871,"uid":69090,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T13:23:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e25b79d25ba5388bacfe08ab582ea373dd592a82","tid":1056871,"uid":62822,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T13:27:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b7de3416f468bed483be376a061d1f813bdc4efc","tid":1056871,"uid":38907,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T13:31:39.000Z","msg":"nut仲好聽過佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16e9370bf4e08b5ef63e679ce7b3de6dfee7dd40","tid":1056871,"uid":132432,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"519d0083e95d60caaa16e7a162cd85450b345923","tid":1056871,"uid":69090,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T13:23:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T13:32:03.000Z","msg":"一睇似打手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"004cdfa7c4ba7bb3f0e606ed2b22f2710a9d6dd7","tid":1